# .raw-exemptions/raw_6.list — grandfather list for raw#6 (folder-naming F4)
# format: <path_prefix_or_file> | <line_range> | <reason> | <expiry YYYY-MM-DD>
# expiry REQUIRED — indefinite grandfather forbidden.
#
# raw#6 bans: utils helpers common lib misc stuff base
# F4 scanner = basename-only match. valid module paths containing these
# segments (infrastructure/common/, libs/helpers/) are whitelisted here.
# Matching is path-prefix: any path starting with the listed prefix is exempt.
#
# 2026-04-21 seed entries — 12 repeated false-positives from raw_all bypass log
# (raw:folder-naming excluded 12+ times). expiry 2026-10-21 = 6 months to let
# scanner become path-aware (follow-up on raw#6).

infrastructure/ | * | valid module namespace — not a generic-dir violation | 2026-10-21
libs/           | * | valid module namespace — not a generic-dir violation | 2026-10-21
# lib/ entry — module-namespace exception (parser-owner runtime container);
# rename to libs/ would break cross-repo import paths in dependent repos
# (hxnccl etc.). audit 2026-04-26: aligned with 12-month review cycle
# (expiry 2027-04-26). owner: hexa-lang
lib/            | * | module-namespace exception (parser-owner runtime container; rename to libs/ would break cross-repo import paths) — owner: hexa-lang | 2027-04-26
